            "value" : "I hope this message finds you well. I've been admiring your work for a while now, and I'm interested in getting a custom tattoo from you.\n\nI have a specific design  that I'd like to have placed on inner part of the upper left arm.\n\nAdditionally, I would like to document the last three minutes of the tattooing process.\n\nCould we possibly schedule a consultation to discuss the design, placement, and the filming aspect?\n\nI'm attaching PDF with more information and details regarding the Tattoo Stencil, Placement, and Evidence video.\n\nLooking forward to the possibility of working with you."
